text: Cathexis longimana is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pascoe in 1859. It is known from Argentina and Brazil.BioLib.cz - Cathexis longimana. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 1859
title: Cathexis longimana
